@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam classBackgroundColor #F1F8E9
skinparam classBorderColor #33691E
skinparam defaultFontSize 13
[*] --> Created
Created --> Closed : review
Closed --> Delivered : confirm
Delivered --> Archived : submit
Archived --> Draft : confirm
Archived : entry / log withdrawal
Closed --> Created : revert
Draft --> [*]
@enduml